<p class="Endnotes"><span id="endnote-024"><a class="_idEndnoteAnchor _idGenColorInherit" href="#endnote-024-backlink">24</a><span class="superscript CharOverride-9"> </span><span class="CharOverride-7">See Erik D. Prince, &ldquo;The MacArthur Model for Afghanistan,&rdquo; </span><span class="CharOverride-8">Wall Street Journal</span><span class="CharOverride-7">, May 31, 2017, available at &lt;www.wsj.com/articles/the-macarthur-model-for-afghanistan-1496269058&gt;; Justin Wise, &ldquo;Blackwater Founder Makes New Pitch for Mercenaries to Take Over Afghan War,&rdquo; </span><span class="CharOverride-8">The Hill</span><span class="CharOverride-7">, July 12, 2018, available at &lt;http://thehill.com/policy/defense/396714-blackwater-founder-proposes-mercenary-takeover-in-afghanistan-amidst-mueller-probe&gt;. </span></span></p>

<p class="Endnotes"><span id="endnote-025"><a class="_idEndnoteAnchor _idGenColorInherit" href="#endnote-025-backlink">25</a><span class="superscript CharOverride-9"> </span><span class="CharOverride-7">John Esterbrook, &ldquo;Rumsfeld: It Would Be a Short War,&rdquo; CBS News, November 15, 2002, available at &lt;www.cbsnews.com/news/rumsfeld-it-would-be-a-short-war/&gt;.</span></span></p>

