<p class="Endnotes"><span id="endnote-043"><a class="_idEndnoteAnchor _idGenColorInherit" href="#endnote-043-backlink">43</a><span class="superscript CharOverride-9"> </span><span class="CharOverride-7">Thomas Erskine Holland, </span><span class="CharOverride-8">The Elements of Jurisprudence, </span><span class="CharOverride-7">9</span><span class="CharOverride-12">th</span><span class="CharOverride-7"> ed. (Oxford: Oxford University Press, 1900), 369</span><span class="CharOverride-13">.</span></span></p>
